e5AvFMYUiCJyjlEQj1NI1OOCgNe5rdC0aIfxhLpWQkalj7mXbVXJu0bZZMs2bxibkSD3xLcDO5bWP72K0LTa-TSU7y7lucpFnfhFQ9pKNjdfzj-dYzmhePbvnerKhWfGJRBi1cjryEhg6MULDL5o5R7YRFHEYCcFRukBBup29n1vu13RbKpogeEP6Z8rTWtn2nYL_tXzpCtzVwO5m2bG6vCDhnVo8V6BTQc--wZpSRm3LRTZLKiHyB_FNGjS9EpmJBsI9bmH8IEVIkFc7jnJRSSNsOoD-D_1-4fq--IBxDDarFhpnHR7XabLqE_ZtT3FwukDKdAiuUcOhcR2vQate-tEvAW7wI/8pSy9UQvomyF6v8dB6LCyi974thukLKo/8" target="_blank"&gt;关税困境&lt;/a&gt;和承诺，以&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/zFzoezw-n2Yd08TjG99eeH28Fi5cZ3xhCTs5tYaEiIJ3h59AlX5Wg9qjxJfAJtmJUGEiKrt5R5unt67fn5sCKh9-AWvReqPS-98kDwyMi7PYYnWi9NjWIo7Ig5LYVmbaMcidwah9u8DYSjcY19igNRw6bjAqrGbq8ZbdpuRPZeHsc4MuIikAXLeUmT1JE47CKhXJfimoALkfbV_WCjR7XVM02NJWXbHIMwhBau4tXyoLY0HtJus2glAaGf3AsKg7WjHxSa8caB4JobfjJEfpUkuPpcgo0twrE6AAlaKTD1YzlE3HmGUwU4zh1Doh5-pyqAJPMkeEsSznqoK0FkVhRsvIjw6x2KRLpjRTRLd0sUXCXLXKL-3kDLFK-ao/HQ5vXptq0L0SfOIMXm1m5iF4cO4_GuwJ/8" target="_blank"&gt;帮助关税袭击出口商&lt;/a&gt;找到当地买家。它还警告各国不要与美国达成惊人的协议，这可能会&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/AFORZJLiGGXKbbaDiTQQhf7EXFgdeG8YfBVNatuQJ0M2Gg43ODf-ULcMqPjr-v6zBTQtBeGrWs9V5xGmCxlfN4WjmMqD85RWacgqOaV28T8fSD6aTH8SdmjOs8XTWLfo3ZrBPEmkOdyZev8-Ld7iuONOBM6FVb112Ecm6Xb13yZ2omC__tWduApVH9bAarUnqzHAAlqjYVRhEubo4bU2kZzcKbNI1X_vZAjwkytRXWHHxyBF3ARasgkrmVHZS5Mtm9yuhpFthtVkO8ZWhssEV_NcUvkCD_uKt9enU-l2jYk8tgWWx0N9kAtDsvaOBF5XO5UDrwRTcYZRvkYFImHmHXHsBVrkjHBxHWZWcG6B3QRkA1Hzk1WCvht5pCM/2z82GPZS54ncekMmikFAPME5mBwXOf_X/8" target="_blank"&gt;损害北京的利益&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;他的顶级经济学家说，特朗普正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Y-ewGsM9oaOcKYJuCUqLls0feTRGs9LlchN0C9K_mR0LscgZtJI1drzT7yeLkFRcURNTIU89qwdmMDb1_5DufJlaguNOh7NaqHoJPhZx4EiqZYn-TFzj3r2MjKgOWMF1x9KH2hj25PwaXozwWRoWrE8reGVGFDr_F9_mgNGCCOuDN36x9wmzKOXk-qJcVWb2B5Ph6vn-BvCn-f4LVUu03Sk-k6a7rtIhq9fIAPsLRZLsCmz73woRGtq4Vnc37MucPGa9BKpi00dUEW1P03EpWMuzVCQX6ja86VO_5HN6T2Pfqsg5nrK-gdyAEdLQbWowh4UsQeWuBX5Wfzw657KIsQStfE0mgnr4n3uWtv1S9vvLgZKUdGFP63psuj0/N4_JUNjQbfBlqNkMeT3zUQmnu8RU2OF1/8" target="_blank"&gt;研究&lt;/a&gt;他是否能够&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/I251d6XRP9OlA6-d5oUhLXRBakg2IxoTUvl35wMv82D_qeuh2mSDnsHq4ns6uhJUvCXXYWn_W1Z-t4xiofuDkZHlE8gBEIbC88tsH6wn4CYVyxRo3wYyOGgZmbW1BTXfLRgiZFjmUKy6Qw0NY8t18f7HjAn25qVuuNcLsbeh62hzZyIpTRRp1K2XgKtiqAWqLaU6-zoPYUxQ5x7Ao6pkIHxuwFQKStStx2JlMo9pp9332YYiEg74HWRiaZWzm_Tdd-c7DgV8av-hfEe53L_OTEd_BwU2j6tlatZdYXhG0dGSmOIGd6P19EYt0FYftmE3tjYNU7YU0M8df5OQZw_47of_t3VI9khUCuwivfRm8gAhhW8hc61NqYVYEyg/3GV9GHD88cbiDM17cJn9IchVF7PfM0UK/8" target="_blank"&gt;解雇美联储主席&lt;/a&gt;杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell），美联储官员警告不要遏制&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/veG1aFcDYCLvKFuregiDYNNqHJT8ebuh5193OeZVHwUnTA3kCcuKNKkaevgq6CxC_ZhcMwxetXlOKtkNMMgOq4f1jgy6-g54IV36bya9f8mbLMfwPYKXmS_FoBZnYvU3MdEhPfIyvpQLDpEvgTdXLsI7gdsc7ltLonoRaq7BTBz95avE11gQod5s6vPsKhRBhjkSv6Ec3ffYYnp3XKghgf1qbmMmlqCvadLx4ocu3jFYwhxdAN7qFwRau5WyQi-tfYd25zMqWvJhan_asDIbOKnZVnvoNlP8EtvndYbbPQWqSiuhfi0nUknKc6bmc1bZgisRfm-eMw59ykp4L0fl9_w7RPkyyPh75DWNIDIkweG-JlFcMUUz-7XGJis/xVqgNpE8zS0311HSFrUxCcoMy2bnAn5n/8" target="_blank"&gt;中央银行独立&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;中央银行前景&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;全球中央银行将在未来几个月内准备削减利率，以使其经济与特朗普的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/x8iavjujy33PP-RUyy-_LcthFJhd45EjCMPzN1LWRmfsme-cLUlR0SbbXKE8briYbxFkErp8clmY7v_uLB84ijyMgW3-oLMODV-3fS-DHQ5xi55dPKMlHMJxyWMh62nREmbUQCGIAdTdZNk4-9cn7GbEVHg2VwfqpNoyInatuw_l3VGX6l-mCsJ4Q6-pQFcbYVuwWzr-Vj8JQmP1gT82Fwsun-xp21Wewh3P2VhXEPKHMtPhzpXuSUONGhR3rLMUN0sbonJxMcgXfltcsD1Ej3MJnP_NwDYvMVSbFkmnY4ZuVyIB9bI4bMQYzFALP3qdrFq7KrzqfpaF0QZqDbXR7CMqiM7R9FcIjAxmBb7cD4WnM9qOYPBxggYcpOc/IHImTD6jwqt3bpSYOwPAXaJajAY_ky6t/8" target="_blank"&gt;贸易战&lt;/a&gt;相提并论。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;尽管实施不断变化，但他的关税到目前为止的增长前景降低了，并增加了美国衰退的风险。世贸组织已经预测，今年&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lG2I9k6iYgpQ2LXhiJgSNiFVrqZKotyjE9BJMA_H3SzrGy-XU-vZ3Mbf6dF-KKxw7Al9Ae9wvfPBLI5RNZGRpkQZw1c6wMZXW8cqGnHSf9QwHh1TEWACrg3wOtGexNkEu9NC_j4nJc2CeoqplzRFBDD76lXHl_OT0B0Mf0jVn5SCaL46X4-TitKP5qSDnLPl-_mIn8FQJxdOJJLuFVc9F-x_vE-KblDT4AmWae4rN1DEucpg2rrVJPVAeDdSkgFpExkjxTdI3m0Fc8xFONMCHTYURDrL0QhTnNl9bxvycF0TCe78KDKAJtp7HmEN7-6aBN0vMrjHYZbPYrTH61oKgvie3lRX450ITDIFpUFiof1RtxRe_86nkY8VVZs/se68_npQ6V_KAUSB9klXEn_rn3f5xtnh/8" title="世贸组织将全球贸易展望削减了特朗普关税中断（1）"&gt;国际商务的下降&lt;/a&gt;，IMF将在本周&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/gY_q3dDO4ixNnAFeSEU4pONQqlmwA7L5W4R1uUObOXGyANXcNYVJfIUps3E84WwY_YcsNqJF_Tu-qmZ1YgdUIF3SXxa6DHXnKDPERsyMzSPVV2lCKFZjpQ7BsjKvWFO6rNyqoTLXqbpWCyKT99vi_xNNvnCFNO5rz4IZ2M8bswU95ZwdhwiPp9MJteNeTC5uUlVR4Uw-WZfoMcAi3cwNLjLBIjEAkqa1bCXu2MtpA2zB-6cgjx7iKj-v43biKSgEw-MXqCDcnuyJTAKpstJyQQ_dzdmwnnc5DyOodeG0Qn962Aw0DNM3iiZZFC0SmQI1PU6AaMqJbnoybM4DGN9CPNKjqC1U-9OaHDXoV8OQEwZWio85EepZK7HIVwA/EwmTyr6irJrRJFp1PCRcAuqJZg9DIiV_/8" title="国际货币基金组织说，贸易“重新启动”以减缓增长，世界躲避经济衰退"&gt;降低其前景&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iz7pVQAVc0FE/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iz7pVQAVc0FE/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;这种背景就是为什么彭博经济学认为，大多数货币官员都准备降低借贷成本，尽管谨慎地减轻了最坏的后果。预计其高级经济率的综合度量将在年底之前下降约一半。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;谨慎地踩踏的情况是需要防止通货膨胀压力，要么依靠以前的消费者价格激增，要么从当前的危机中迫在眉睫。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;美联储在那里面临&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/BQPktb-GDO-eQItIZXZ7qJRuRMETjxnyQmOwZT5pc5Gljech-8WnM7XHWESrujDYa7-RHyRk_yJaZKwZ8zDKCswenFLe0yKOPxSL4bDjw0rvkeqsWdXkueyPeXsnAtgr7zNgfhivFiWu0nE23gimS2bB9tZwwYN9gdJ8HWTJOMQBnkSEbPhKGsLmjKEvgxVg-crlz3HP1IPJwIhNZxZhspejtRXdvyrKEW8gSyVgOnKBWXaXbE2G_zt8Ft31TOLtStNK0qcWvMmULjX-XXDUzm54uiLHFohmM8RS5GWVa9_ln_vIVR1UR9QPzJgUASc_PG8t88_FSiSLHesYNZSd7gBk44foNdUNcGTsvMF3IfaX3ALg_MgX8euqwBc/JwtXdC-J4oibf-3_8OfYoE7V7tog_YsS/8" target="_blank"&gt;更大的挑战&lt;/a&gt;。白宫施加的征费很可能会自动提高美国消费者的价格 - 鲍威尔在上周三的演讲中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/NVE_mgyMJKgDRLYlL4TQFkZiBrlqB2XnYgmdX4T2scxY4Y8ZI6mUJdGTwXCSrp08jJEr2dJmPxYxd7ox97HBPt3Bgx4sydVTS3dAfJ0y-bkGCPrRgHtlvnf8d1KVftEB2-4_qv5kWLVX6ALjZLId-zwZsWrKHu-hc-r-QiuUcuMFbQBGTtM1BuzTj4LCNg_Zefdc-uStLB3XTsOuJcmD_YsFo7zuoy4e23MXw33ZaaSNo3jCcVGJMl9OVtzobs0DvQG-YnvHiPw7kgydeYuWU68FnnCbXCMHE6iPb1hvL8L9yt43H7WJBYPEIDLqxS9MQ8U_yrHEGLQgnuwS0xxSEb4lOqwkxjVF2iLHCSRDEmoIZMnVDEtOC6sTEoE/kItNRRRUV_yaFkCy4huWcd4up6nM7CYe/8" target="_blank"&gt;承诺要密切关注&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/gTfLsa0M0wFz4EHmbdET28i5R30uQxyALbHb71jzrpV7wrAD7AWgEEFNbst7lEKm_kFOnCtNod-F_yc7LFpusZozVOKWiXTxeN6_rqbtW_r8IAsKsBn7FrD0t4latY5pip2j5Xapy9xSwbnq3l_Lr-Bn1UyPDKeCuSGSCin_sFW-bDREPGu5hJNoZL1VHQxYvuwbopWwEk0exxg986CfVZKeh0UCkAsCRU9X7rYu132b_qOF0NpVHpOtqo_HlwS6MKb3i9G3kZvONvi1Gw4ozwHCNyUGe5VfrbZeuT0hvCKEJ3I1EVuFxzz2DuPzLwUt4cwd6psKj-OsvO0l2nK-uSN0tnJiURhF_cOUH2CrBAs7boWO-nCYYbzPQvE/6G9179pyYsioxx51Eom8CUMoojiFrPJU/8" target="_blank"&gt;风险&lt;/a&gt;有一个原因，为什么在美国不设想太多放松。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ivXHRG9eW9zI/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ivXHRG9eW9zI/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;全球同行将注意贸易战中的对策和升级，以评估自己经济中充气的威胁。欧洲中央银行负责人克里斯汀·拉加德（Christine Lagarde）上周说，任何&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/HvtW5Q3bqpwb3tX3CklW3w8vm5uqosuu66DpIiMiV9E0o-HwUbSuzs5b4Ay3gOGGEP-3fezeQWOjUkYu4lxFQ3zYoiwWkbkg0oYA4zeUO17mTKTPWN3niSDtdH63MnvESeWOkvz4NciedMeWITnV5_pANvlpRVxEb6EopTNLx_ClKNNunctC36sEHXXNi7j8FGZl64EeLISQEMo6qp9xbMumeYIONe-wYArpZ3ImQXTiFNblZa9Azz2L0dm1Uon6slHemYVL2x8OUeNUTsnDMUWCUh0SVmgQqPgJWIieDTGzIXHAbAzdD7Px1dpQxAGZyvifqOEXJ19JyhyB3lD-pw9w3W8Bb1AUvIqr9nlZBfNe0GfPXT_hMup1UuM/p0v5B5dUzqgfH31AByKtghLLJqAQMMKt/8" target="_blank"&gt;价格效果&lt;/a&gt;“只会在随着时间的流逝中变得更加清晰”。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;由于对美国决策的完整性的疑问，货币波动率较弱，可能证明对某些人（例如&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/wHYY7rymkmBXQJ5IaochNp6QzBjw0uTO6PMbH4Ki_RvVFGAKDIsPJFrVr03F5DPkoMqAULwgPPo_cocDn4kt4PHPlNEgXZdglzozAHlWso9kRyBCh80rDJarijIY3R_BJQPvdUrqompkCO9_83Wty5mLluD9QC79Z9ma7l-LhOQy2_xwADbfqSKOzVNQwkZlNeMk-7ArHZWixBMVJYJ3HMf4TQ--fhaXGoXtPa2MpMb9c6q4mNlBenTiKYwWrWxeJPUq9hOugPg9U6cbF67giz_-0k7og-mlXreVcYV1Yb4fFOXd8joUabGsm6OXMVp6n2eGByg6PrtmG2s2EdxTaMu0-1S0G8qLx8uMmEe15Rcts-Fyah7upRnEdrI/3VbwizbH0VUuGpqqEr2ZgewivavkNCTY/8" title="SNB认为抵制在争夺法郎收益的冲动的冲动"&gt;瑞士人）&lt;/a&gt;进行了额外的测试。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;然而，世界各地的货币政策都消失了，目前官员的可见性令人震惊地低落，这会使特朗普多变的异想天开的困难加剧。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;尽管如此，BE在最新版的《我们的季刊指南》中为全球23个中央银行的最新季度指南中的发展尽可能多，占全球经济的90％。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/B74q4w5aG9UlKqVamCPVZyUgVDdk5WiqhUkzwEu8HoKdSd1moe_s_LqZtcll8_ik4nUlllm12ZJ2_D17mYBfXzwkq