HBFdfxIU/iLDXmchNnErM/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;华盛顿特区的最高法院大楼。&lt;em&gt;摄影师：Stefani Reynolds/Bloomberg&lt;/em&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普政府&lt;/strong&gt;要求最高法院&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/y3ln4oeft3nYxlm4XqmRyokObB_qYA3yygVjZfDjblnmHMDBEd2jtfQQJ6kdzLy3qoLwalktYBpxL-J5IXP_kb3bEBAiwNNFAFwbSFBfWFfAN5f5gAaPwNHxKrlOIbF-ehZjWSc91NDvnkvu_Sv8dIN_mMHMoKL5T0VZYc4AzuqbQUeZ2607-88vSolgKfdmvdm4tCLB1jPUocBFzDrHpg0VdGg0MU07y1fj6FxAaXZ5FshFUE0NH2zJI6FBEtIzff4v18UJFWRy6fPMzYgyk8rXZfWPu684VwMfDBdYhhGrRveVgjfm2ovTc0Isf_IkGNlKk872DLIEsWqLXxDP8iV9VbL7Q6kQcnIVBbdYY28QfZtmcbEvLiDCmhw/FUdr-qHyZm77fM17n4IdUm82man6Ss2e/8" target="_blank"&gt;撤销其决定&lt;/a&gt;将委内瑞拉人驱逐出境的决定，归萨尔瓦多臭名昭著的监狱。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;高等法院在周六上午1点左右在华盛顿进行了干预&lt;/strong&gt;，此前被拘留者提出紧急要求&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/4x0oksRYVc9mgI2rbkaZ0hJzKiLTxRw2Kcy6yMQQzjrUXFRoRegO8vAJ6Nooj2pFF3LWQbeSnn6xBeWgnoMQ9fupRaIPMwsOpJJJ2u8IGFOsya8xfHK5j_Bbl2-JJ9H0w9tw4_hgcTQtXfZq_bibhmo_QruXuOj1bcDUB91KqOsiJRWr3nQPp8PBD9EXiSZ1H3ybhvfPlhjrFycO9u6HLBPwezd539BV1bv7_BmZ3v9_yreWPjEWUQC5Ud3UU9pzR7Z2-z48a3yk7dj8_rcWKYpVuluv8rHbJsCxwGf35mzrlDLgNcAeI9Ad_ZtGn435LtNBvDweGYMtsXXfvKEx3qhjsDtbxkO1BZDispcetklPGv5PsUzA8xFioDw/ej-WxIiY4NDSkra3aElunUb98IMTzKZr/8" target="_blank"&gt;将其驱逐出境从德克萨斯州安森市的蓝带拘留中心驱逐出境&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;法官塞缪尔·阿利托（Samuel Alito）&lt;/strong&gt;和克拉伦斯·托马斯（Clarence Thomas）表示反对，阿利托（Alito）说，法院采取了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/sFUlbtk96-OBhQDcTQXYsE13fXRoizcB0RfRydKeScCoEKaFoCV--gwRkBpfgU80eU-OrVcAstTv61cEDhcp6gMjn_xP2w-OJD6T_0nqBU0qM_raRJaIoiSagUlKbqaCOuLkX7ZKI7GCs50tdq51Q6Ma0N41COe6jjdAGuzl17S2_qWRN--coCn73vYTTU9JfYltYTbJQSMtzlPqxAx4gPv9e3s09ff0c8P5gueySpDubMD3LwrqajIO1ZGbqOgwho8s3qBVckzPhbNuio4McUlplVu1MQe8G3C3kSwqSkyhCQ3LXRc6w0rwIBFrQtMmW5V7fDta_Cwig-h5N_737rBHWnEZdBVwIfSBCWlgyM_RBtDCsmzvDFoUNxk/jCKV8jWftX8GlJ1ZmUe8Qq2TYptNIv0c/8" target="_blank"&gt;“前所未有且在法律上有疑问”的理由&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;驱逐出境&lt;/strong&gt;是面临挑战的许多特朗普政府政策之一。上周，最高法院表示&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/fENKq7Qdl7nbnsMWovtGzvSoLW3K8wx1ODfSn87lQyd0DxH7f3-Mitwy3yOwu48gv3S1naxxJr9sKPSpquIZUQ-69Of_rRc1rracFW1ksQ-I-eY12710Ybj9-dISpKU2IBNZGsIUcRB6GgDlNi9skK8C-1Pr1injAwtAVPr6AkFL36ytlsKlJyIlFZ8Hv4469IeAeqg3dSJzzopjU5hsFsFB_SymtqWLBivEXOuVPQyJK1l1d9L9hAD2eA22JZItLSRhTBhvKAkizNH6B4hEJ0Mu92tLTJ_wz5xvJdSmzgOMi_jhbA99mJUkRomFeQraDj-TMuB-bPaye4k7hMMyT91tkBb58T6T1NoRZydUe0gvTJu2DN1CPQvfMxI/wE16UNEqrlO3DTmNg3VFdV8mUvFM5GU1/8" target="_blank"&gt;，将听取有关特朗普开始限制自动出生权公民身份的争论&lt;/a&gt;，这可能会颠覆长期的宪法权利。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;自从他第二任期以来，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普一直在测试&lt;/strong&gt;他对移民的权力的界限。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/d8udGT83vIOKhDGUVr0o2YNegofJ-GKJWrrLyIY31VCDUkUsq0yWXFl8CsXLMRM2CjMWWflLFoyowTWQ8iBh9VS-OVq5iTMsP40i0oCznc6dDYn5krKXrzRzyULy_-nI55kNa-Jt3xheS1rteDxViWZ1VFW5MN99SwQxPIHfBG0gKu7EWWx_bUTvIxu3NYxALThqIFOB0K6zE43pvJoh5ok4IYgMHSdZhLTafTI49ZrJbqHokodaxdlB8354nVKuRCxUuNbU9q7iZ_Jk777m4pMd3ExLVGC8HIMCJ8quuGayAtJ4VX62RZUnv0D8QbBY79h0RTQcujlE8ice7q581_VyqYmTzOUYxJTx6ziXETfBchcpBOAm4pLGgAw/Oca64_CJx-YuQ9RhcaozG8JibGP16oEx/8" target="_blank"&gt;这是我们驱逐出萨尔瓦多的Quicktake&lt;/a&gt; 。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse